Company Overview of EnCap Energy Capital Fund V, L.P.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
EnCap Energy Capital Fund V, L.P. specializes in growth capital. It seeks to invest in oil and gas reserves, gas processing plants or pipelines. The fund prefers to invest in United States and Canadian. The fund typically invests between $2 million and $15 million.


