EnCap Energy Capital Fund VIII, L.P.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 23, 2017 8:48 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of EnCap Energy Capital Fund VIII, L.P.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
EnCap Energy Capital Fund VIII, L.P. specializes in seed, start ups, early venture, and growth capital investments. The fund seeks to invest in the energy sector with a focus on small to mid-cap upstream oil and gas sectors. It invests in companies engaged in acquisition and exploitation of oil and gas reserves, the development of low-risk drilling opportunities in known producing regions and/or the application of advanced drilling and completion technologies to conventional and unconventional reservoirs in the United States and Canada. The fund prefers to invest in North America. It seeks to invest between $50 million and $300 million. EnCap Energy Capital Fund VIII, L.P. is comprised of En...
EnCap Energy Capital Fund VIII, L.P. specializes in seed, start ups, early venture, and growth capital investments. The fund seeks to invest in the energy sector with a focus on small to mid-cap upstream oil and gas sectors. It invests in companies engaged in acquisition and exploitation of oil and gas reserves, the development of low-risk drilling opportunities in known producing regions and/or the application of advanced drilling and completion technologies to conventional and unconventional reservoirs in the United States and Canada. The fund prefers to invest in North America. It seeks to invest between $50 million and $300 million. EnCap Energy Capital Fund VIII, L.P. is comprised of EnCap Energy Capital Fund VIII, L.P. and EnCap VIII Co-Investment Fund LP (a.k.a EnCap Energy Capital VIII co-investors) a parallel fund.
Detailed Description


1100 LouisianaSuite 4900Houston, TX 77002United StatesFounded in 2010



Phone: 713-659-6100

Fax: 713-659-6130








